               </div>
               <div class="flex gap-4">
                  <span
                     class="w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold text-white"
                     >2</span
                  >
                  <div>
                     <p class="text-zinc-300 font-medium">Install App</p>
                     <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-1">
                        Extract the ZIP. Install the <code
                           class="bg-zinc-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-zinc-200"
                           >.deb</code
                        > package (Ubuntu/Debian) or build from source (Arch).
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="flex gap-4">
                  <span
                     class="w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold text-white"
                     >3</span
                  >
                  <div>
                     <p class="text-zinc-300 font-medium">Install Connector</p>
                     <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-1">
                        Load the <code class="text-zinc-300">extension</code> folder
                        in your browser's extension settings (Developer Mode).
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="flex gap-4">
                  <span
                     class="w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold text-white"
