         <div
            id="build-guide"
            class="mt-16 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
         >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
               <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
               >
                  <path
                     stroke-linecap="round"
                     stroke-linejoin="round"
                     stroke-width="2"
                     d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
               </svg>
               <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
                  Building from Source (macOS)
               </h3>
            </div>

            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6 text-sm">
               Since we don't have a pre-built installer for macOS yet, you can
               easily build and run the app yourself. Requires <a
                  href="https://nodejs.org"
                  class="text-purple-400 hover:underline">Node.js</a
               > and <a
                  href="https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install"
                  class="text-purple-400 hover:underline">Rust</a
               >.
            </p>

            <div
               class="bg-black/50 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-300 overflow-x-auto border border-zinc-800"
            >
               <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <p class="text-zinc-500"># 1. Clone the repository</p>
                  <p>
                     git clone
                     https://github.com/christianpe1/lyrics-overlay.git
                  </p>
                  <p>cd lyrics-overlay</p>

                  <p class="text-zinc-500 mt-2"># 2. Install dependencies</p>
                  <p>npm install</p>
                  <p>cd server && npm install && npm start</p>

                  <p class="text-zinc-500 mt-2"># 3. Run in development mode (On another terminal)</p>
                  <p class="text-purple-400">npm run tauri dev</p>
               </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500">
               <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
               >
                  <path
                     stroke-linecap="round"
                     stroke-linejoin="round"
